hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: The project should be an original idea with creative design and/or implementation. Did it use a particularly clever technique?
The project should be functional and have a reasonable amount of working parts in the 12 hour time frame that was given. Does the hack work? Did the team achieve everything they wanted?
The project should have a clear intended purpose. Extra points awarded to teams that solved a real world problem.

hackathon-location-address: 110 Kingston Ln, Monmouth Junction, NJ 08852, USA
hackathon-description-header: HackSB is a 12-hour hackathon at the South Brunswick Public Library. Join us in building awesome software and hardware projects.
